{"tid":2222198,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文/分析]其實係咪真係有正常人會玩原神?","createTime":"2020-09-29T02:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T01:00:17.000Z","uid":123264,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ef7c121c8d6455b13b341cce903dc16d39f1fa5a","tid":2222198,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"講真 本身出左個trailer 話隻game抄Zelda我都有小小擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為如果真係抄Zelda又擺一堆錢落去既話 點垃圾都有限度<br />\n佢畫風又確實係好睇 仲要係全平台免費開放世界遊戲 又上Switch 又要上埋xbox pc 都有小小驚強國可以出到一隻好game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢出左之後真係得啖笑<br />\n睇左兩眼gameplay同系統分析 佢根本就無開放世界 基本上就係mmo形式既課金手遊<br />\n人物出率仲低過臭名昭著既fgo<br />\n人物技能方面好似要一個人物出五 六次先有得出齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊戲劇情 故事方面完全唔存在 配音弱智又尷尬<br />\ngameplay基本上同普通mmo一樣係刷副本出野打怪 但你變強就要課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n講真 要普通玩慣左主機遊戲既玩家要用7-8小時去玩呢隻game根本就係折磨<br />\n呢d game 正常既主機玩家根本睇唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上如果唔係強國果班玩慣左垃圾既白痴都無可能去玩呢隻game<br />\n呢隻game係免費遊戲 但就算你課左五千蚊以上 都未必有普通60$單機遊戲既體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主機玩家睇唔上 受眾就一定係留番比強國果班有手機無電腦既小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗原神間公司都係咁樣定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻game基本上就算係連一部分強國遊戲玩家都話垃圾 要抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />主要原因係因為強國人唔中意佢抄襲但又話自己係國產之光 係名符其實既狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你係香港見到有fd玩 咁其實你連屌都唔駛屌 呢種人基本上係平時用一半以上人工課落手遊既人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢想浪費金錢同生命 其實你由得佢就好 佢一係就用一 兩百個鍾頭變強 一係就瘋狂課金 一係浪費時間 一係浪費金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你由得佢玩<br />\n<br />\n以上係我對原神既分析 但因為我本人費事dl隻game (手機成6gb 電腦我又驚佢幫我裝360)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以可能唔準確 如果有烈士玩過既可以補充<br />\n咁當然白痴game都有白痴既受眾 特別係強國<br />\n好似王者榮耀咁都搞到有聲有色<br />\n但個手遊會唔會係手機玩家圈子之外做大? 我覺得一定唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但當然呢種時候就見到某d台灣/香港youtuber走出黎吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢種人係為左views定係收左錢 我就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但最應該抵制既一定係呢種垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7332d5561aea000a24751e36be0c1837ede591","tid":2222198,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:42:34.000Z","msg":"TLDR; 隻game係史詩級垃圾手遊"},{"pid":"c6c04a0ba3289648b90a497f943cfd001e0236ab","tid":2222198,"uid":378141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=204028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D204028&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXNekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=b4d09555\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=204028</a><br />\n原神有後門程式 被網民發現後承諾刪除之"},{"pid":"2251b20cd201376379f1204bd2aa1c63a4263f25","tid":2222198,"uid":31374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:46:38.000Z","msg":"係得支那賤蓄先會將mobile game放係PS4上面玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048eae6234847ecdd934ac8324c972b7270c5801","tid":2222198,"uid":378141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6c04a0ba3289648b90a497f943cfd001e0236ab","tid":2222198,"uid":378141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=204028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D204028&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXN